  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the best IAS coaching institutes in Mumbai?",
  "response": "Choosing the best IAS coaching institute can depend on various factors such as teaching methodology, faculty, study materials, and past results. Here are some of the top IAS coaching institutes in Mumbai that are generally well-regarded:\n\n1. **The Prayas India**\n   - Known for its comprehensive courses and experienced faculty.\n   - Offers both online and offline classes.\n   - Notable for personalized attention and mentorship programs.\n\n2. **Paradise IAS Academy**\n   - Highly reputed for its strong focus on current affairs and answer writing practice.\n   - Known for its detailed test series and mock interviews.\n   - Offers a wide range of optional subjects.\n\n3. **Pinnacle IAS Academy**\n   - Renowned for its integrated and holistic approach to IAS preparation.\n   - Offers small batch sizes for better student-teacher interaction.\n   - Emphasizes on both Prelims and Mains preparation.\n\n4. **Chanakya IAS Academy**\n   - One of the oldest and most trusted institutes in Mumbai.\n   - Known for its experienced faculty and comprehensive study material.\n   - Offers various test series and performance evaluation.\n\n5. **Career Launcher**\n   - Known for its innovative teaching methods and focus on technology-driven learning.\n   - Provides a wide array of resources including recorded lectures and doubt-solving sessions.\n   - Has a strong record of producing successful candidates.\n\n6. **Rau's IAS Study Circle**\n   - Known for its well-structured courses and extensive study material.\n   - Offers personalized guidance and mentorship programs.\n   - Has a strong reputation for producing toppers.\n\nWhen choosing an institute, consider visiting their websites, reading reviews, and if possible, talking to current or former students to get a better sense of which institute might be the best fit for your needs.",
